## ðŸš€ Whatâ€™s New in 1.0.2

- ðŸ”¹ Core system moved into a separate file: `NanoMVCCore.php`, introducing the new base class `nmvc_core`
- ðŸ”¹ `NanoMVC.php` now simply extends it via `class nmvc extends nmvc_core {}` â€” allows safe customization
- ðŸ”¹ **Case-insensitive routing**: Controller names in URLs are no longer case-sensitive
- ðŸ”¹ Access original URL casing inside controllers:
  `$this->_get_controller()` and `$this->_get_action()`
- ðŸ”¹ Autoloaded models now support parameters via config
- ðŸ”¹ Redesigned welcome view template
- ðŸ”¹ **PostgreSQL support** in the PDO plugin
  - Includes support for `port` and `schema` options
  - Improved `num_rows()` and `last_query()` methods (now includes bound parameters)
- ðŸ”¹ Minor bug fixes and cleanup

